1.frontend: angular2
2.backend:
    2.1 connects to angular2: 
    node.js, 
    Express.js(create RESTFul services), 
    Nodemon(monitor for any changes in source and auto restart serer and reload code)
    authentication:  PassportJS utilizing JWT

    2.2 connects to apache spark:
        option A: RESTFul: Livy or spark-jobserver
            (node.js - livy or spark-jobserver - database)
        option B: apache spark grab data from database, then update info into database. 
            (node.js - database - apache spark)

3. database: MongoDB